Package AbmModel

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MandatorySimModel
    The interface of acceptable mandatory simulation model for ABM All mandatory data structures that ABM can deal with should implement this API A mandatory model is an essential concept for a simulation
    OptionalSimModel
    The interface of acceptable optional simulation model for ABM All optional data structures that ABM can deal with should implement this API An optional model is not an essential concept for a simulation It brings additional information to the scenario and they can be ignored by choice
    SimModel
    The interface of acceptable simulation model for ABM All data structures that ABM can deal with should implement this API
